00:08:48.679 --> 00:08:57.120
This video is now available in English on jw.org and will be available in other languages

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:59.440
soon.

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:03.120
Please take the time to watch it.

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:08.679
No doubt you'd agree that it takes effort to remain vigilant.

00:09:08.679 --> 00:09:11.519
But how can that benefit us?

00:09:11.519 --> 00:09:17.360
Do you recall what we read earlier in Proverbs 28-14?

00:09:17.360 --> 00:09:24.000
